comment: Ingles (UTA) grabs and holds Aldridge (POR) while setting a backscreen and prevents him from defending the drive to the basket.
Ingles (UTA) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) arm and the contact affects his play to the basket.
RATR and L-Slash show Burke (UTA) grab Crabbe's (POR) arm and prevents him from securing the loose ball.
Aldridge (POR) sets the screen on Millsap (UTA) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Favors (UTA) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) body and the contact affects his shot.
Gobert (UTA) sets the screen on Crabbe (POR) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Aldridge (POR) bumps Burke (UTA) after the shot but the contact is incidental.
Wright (POR) sets the screen on Ingles (UTA) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Gobert (UTA) blocks Aldridge's (POR) layup attempt after it hits the backboard.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a goaltending violation was upheld.
Afflalo (POR) commits a take foul on Ingles (UTA).
Ingles (UTA) grabs Aldridge's (POR) arm while trying to reach in for the steal.
Lillard (POR) legally contests the jumpshot by Favors (UTA).
